<Default><b>[GORILLA WARRIOR]
Hey, Sein!</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:18.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:24.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a mage passing through.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:24.820 --> 00:00:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said he's got time
to take our photo if we hurry!</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:27.490 --> 00:00:28.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never heard of it.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:29.030 --> 00:00:30.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A photo. What's that?</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Hm.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:34.830 --> 00:00:41.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sein grunts]</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:46.340 --> 00:00:47.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
Just come on!</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry!</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:50.550 --> 00:00:51.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Sein grunts]
-[Gorilla Warrior laughs]</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:54.100 --> 00:00:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be an adventure!</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:55.930 --> 00:00:57.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The start of our legend!</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:57.640 --> 00:01:04.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000017
00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000018
00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:18.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:57.100 --> 00:03:03.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000020
00:03:04.230 --> 00:03:06.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You said this guy's
a strong warrior, right?</b></Default>

c0000021
00:03:06.980 --> 00:03:08.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a dwarf who's stood guard</b></Default>

c0000022
00:03:08.310 --> 00:03:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over the next village
for almost 400 years.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:03:10.650 --> 00:03:12.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know they live a long time,</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:12.110 --> 00:03:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but what's their
life expectancy?</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:14.490 --> 00:03:16.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Usually about three centuries.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a long-lived friend
of mine.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:18.910 --> 00:03:20.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone calls him
Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:23.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to chat with him
one more time before he dies.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:26.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Wow, you're all heart, huh?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:26.830 --> 00:03:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A rare opportunity.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:30.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There probably
aren't many people</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:30.170 --> 00:03:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who can talk about
the past with you.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:31.880 --> 00:03:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see why you're
looking forward to it.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:34.170 --> 00:03:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose I can accept a detour
if it's that important to you.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:40.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, Fern.
We'll stay for a decade or so.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:40.970 --> 00:03:43.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] We're staying
one week at most.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:04:03.620 --> 00:04:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that the village?</b></Default>

c0000039
00:04:11.330 --> 00:04:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:04:13.710 --> 00:04:14.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been a while.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:19.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see?
I did my best with the stories,</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:19.260 --> 00:04:21.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but nothing could live up
to the real thing.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:23.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This guy looks too old
to stand up.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:25.890 --> 00:04:28.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Remind me.
Who are you, again?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:28.730 --> 00:04:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
He's totally decrepit.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, it's me, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:37.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Ah, yes,
I remember you now.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:38.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:39.200 --> 00:04:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the point
in pretending to be senile?</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thwacks]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:48.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most deaths in battle</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:50.210 --> 00:04:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>come from the careless
underestimation</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:52.210 --> 00:04:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of your opponent.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:53.420 --> 00:04:55.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Arrogance is
the greatest weakness</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:55.460 --> 00:04:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of people and demons alike.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:57.340 --> 00:04:58.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:58.840 --> 00:04:59.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
Trouble standing?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:05:00.380 --> 00:05:02.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't matter
how strong you are.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:04.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An injury can be
the end of anyone.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:05:04.930 --> 00:05:07.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially if that person
doesn't defend themselves.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:09.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000063
00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:11.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
If I had drawn my sword,</b></Default>

c0000064
00:05:11.940 --> 00:05:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'd be down one leg,
young man.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:05:15.190 --> 00:05:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Your strategies
are as underhanded as ever.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:18.820 --> 00:05:20.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, indeed.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:20.530 --> 00:05:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good to see you, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:22.450 --> 00:05:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, make yourself at home.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:25.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:26.620 --> 00:05:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Wait. Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:29.370 --> 00:05:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't walk.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:31.370 --> 00:05:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's fine.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:32.330 --> 00:05:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll be training here
with him anyway.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:35.130 --> 00:05:36.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Right.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:36.750 --> 00:05:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That old man
is really something else.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crickets chirping]</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:40.510 --> 00:05:41.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 16A ]
And you're more than welcome</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:43.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to use the firewood.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:43.550 --> 00:05:45.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Fern? If we're going
to be here for ten years,</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:45.890 --> 00:05:47.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll need to find some work.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:47.270 --> 00:05:48.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
We talked about this.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:48.810 --> 00:05:50.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're staying
for a week, remember?</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:51.350 --> 00:05:52.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Okay, fine.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:57.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[leaves rustling]</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:01.490 --> 00:06:04.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:04.660 --> 00:06:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 16B]
This is a small village.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sometimes we struggle
to find help</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the harvest,
so thank you.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:15.580 --> 00:06:17.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like we have
anything else to do.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:19.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, anyway...</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:20.090 --> 00:06:22.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this is the happiest
I've ever seen Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:23.130 --> 00:06:24.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until your party arrived,</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:24.430 --> 00:06:26.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't know that
he had any friends.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:27.050 --> 00:06:28.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a senile old man.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:29.020 --> 00:06:30.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Conversations
are a struggle for him.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:32.060 --> 00:06:34.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's defended the village
from monsters and demons</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:34.270 --> 00:06:35.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for longer
than we've been alive,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:37.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but no one even knows why.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's like our protective deity.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:42.530 --> 00:06:44.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So he's always
been lonely, then.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:44.570 --> 00:06:45.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:47.330 --> 00:06:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000104
00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] A week really
flies by, doesn't it?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:07:27.610 --> 00:07:28.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is Stark?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL] He's improved
a great deal for one week.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:07:32.540 --> 00:07:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Humans develop quickly.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:35.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
They do.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:37.710 --> 00:07:39.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been meaning to say
thank you, by the way.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:40.380 --> 00:07:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
Hm?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:44.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't understand back then,
but I'm grateful now.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:45.130 --> 00:07:46.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All those years ago,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:49.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you gave me a reason to get
to know Himmel and the others.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:51.260 --> 00:07:53.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] What made you
decide to take this post,</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:53.140 --> 00:07:54.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Old Man Voll?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:54.930 --> 00:07:56.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
It's ancient history now.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:57.640 --> 00:07:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doesn't matter. Not anymore.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:08:00.730 --> 00:08:02.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People don't often
risk their lives</b></Default>

c0000119
00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for something
that doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:08:04.110 --> 00:08:05.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:08.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was my wife.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:08:09.030 --> 00:08:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the village she loved.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:08:11.740 --> 00:08:13.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will protect it until I die.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:13.950 --> 00:08:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000125
00:08:17.540 --> 00:08:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
She was a human.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm keeping a promise
to someone</b></Default>

c0000127
00:08:21.580 --> 00:08:23.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the world has long forgotten.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:26.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Through this act, I remember.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:29.510 --> 00:08:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry. But I won't say
anything further.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:35.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could I describe her?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:35.640 --> 00:08:39.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her face, her voice,
the light I saw in her eyes?</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:40.150 --> 00:08:43.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is my memory,
and I will carry it alone.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:44.770 --> 00:08:46.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounds silly, doesn't it?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:46.820 --> 00:08:48.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keeping a promise to the dead.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:48.950 --> 00:08:51.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guarding a home
she'd no longer recognize.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:53.580 --> 00:08:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Yes, it does.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:56.660 --> 00:08:57.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it still matters.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:59.330 --> 00:09:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Living or dead, you made
a promise to someone you love.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'd be glad to know
you've kept it.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:07.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel...</b></Default>

c0000141
00:09:07.510 --> 00:09:09.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have the makings
of a great hero.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:09:10.380 --> 00:09:13.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt that
you'll defeat the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:09:14.430 --> 00:09:17.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My wife's greatest wish
was to lead an ordinary life</b></Default>

c0000144
00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the era of peace that
the defeat of the Demon King</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:22.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would surely
have brought about.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:22.810 --> 00:09:24.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I look forward
to the day of your victory.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:25.610 --> 00:09:29.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will carry your memory
as I have carried hers.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:29.650 --> 00:09:31.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't get me wrong.
I love the idea,</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:31.780 --> 00:09:34.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you have more
important memories to focus on.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:36.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And our stories are covered.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:36.790 --> 00:09:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren and Eisen
will know them.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:41.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] I won't live
nearly as long as she will.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:43.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yes.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:43.170 --> 00:09:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess it'll be your job, then.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:45.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] You'll be the one
to carry our memories</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into the future.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:50.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Won't you?</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:51.630 --> 00:09:53.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess if I have to.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:55.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been blessed
with good companions.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:10:01.770 --> 00:10:03.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Frieren. Remind me later.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a collection
of handsome poses</b></Default>

c0000164
00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to show you
for your recollections.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:09.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] On second thought,
maybe I won't remember you.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:10:13.450 --> 00:10:14.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He showed me the poses,</b></Default>

c0000167
00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I doubt
it was actually necessary.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Almost feels like
a waste of a memory.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
Tell me something.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you remember
that Hero's face?</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:25.250 --> 00:10:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course, I do.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:10:26.840 --> 00:10:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And his voice?</b></Default>

c0000173
00:10:28.380 --> 00:10:29.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:10:30.510 --> 00:10:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, don't insult me.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:10:32.630 --> 00:10:34.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember everything.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:37.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel is the reason I decided
I'd get to know people at all.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:38.850 --> 00:10:41.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like your reason for defending
this village from danger.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:43.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It matters to me.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:45.190 --> 00:10:46.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:46.770 --> 00:10:48.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A reason, huh?</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:48.770 --> 00:10:49.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:51.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't remember.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:52.110 --> 00:10:53.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all gone now.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:54.450 --> 00:10:56.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her face. Her voice.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:57.280 --> 00:10:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The light I saw in her eyes.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:11:00.540 --> 00:11:02.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And yet, I continue.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:11:02.910 --> 00:11:05.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I protect the village
as I swore I would,</b></Default>

c0000188
00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because it matters to me.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:11:07.460 --> 00:11:10.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000190
00:11:10.460 --> 00:11:13.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never knew you had
a sense of humor, Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:11:15.340 --> 00:11:16.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
By the way...</b></Default>

c0000192
00:11:16.800 --> 00:11:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what brings you
all the way out here?</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:19.050 --> 00:11:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is your party headed?</b></Default>

c0000194
00:11:21.100 --> 00:11:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We're going to Aureole.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:23.020 --> 00:11:24.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The land where souls rest.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
And where is that?</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ende, where the Demon King's
castle is.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:33.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[VOLL] I see.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:34.610 --> 00:11:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
So you're finally setting off</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:37.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to defeat the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:39.410 --> 00:11:41.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That era of peace
she talked about.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:42.330 --> 00:11:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope it's everything
she dreamed of.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:53.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Demon King is alrea...</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:53.880 --> 00:11:56.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:12:02.430 --> 00:12:04.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FRIEREN] Hm.
-[VOLL] What is it?</b></Default>

c0000207
00:12:06.520 --> 00:12:08.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just forming a memory.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:11.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something of you to carry
with me into the future.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:12:12.690 --> 00:12:13.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:12:15.280 --> 00:12:16.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sounds nice.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:12:17.280 --> 00:12:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I'd like that.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:12:18.950 --> 00:12:22.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000213
00:12:22.410 --> 00:12:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm very glad I got to see you
at the end of my life.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:12:26.710 --> 00:12:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You said that exact same thing</b></Default>

c0000215
00:12:28.290 --> 00:12:29.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when we spoke 80 years ago.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:35.050 --> 00:12:36.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dog barking]</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:39.260 --> 00:12:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goodbye, Old Man Voll.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:41.390 --> 00:12:42.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take care.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:44.350 --> 00:12:45.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:46.180 --> 00:12:47.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:47.520 --> 00:12:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL] I dreamed
of my wife last night.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:55.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps reminiscing with you
shook something loose</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:55.190 --> 00:12:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that was buried
deep in my memory.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:57.700 --> 00:12:58.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:59.530 --> 00:13:00.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:13:09.500 --> 00:13:16.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000228
00:13:23.180 --> 00:13:24.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What was that about?</b></Default>

c0000229
00:13:24.890 --> 00:13:26.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm looking for someone.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:13:28.350 --> 00:13:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I joined up with your party
for a reason.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:13:30.690 --> 00:13:31.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You remember, right?</b></Default>

c0000232
00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:34.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because it was a lifelong
dream of yours</b></Default>

c0000233
00:13:34.190 --> 00:13:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to travel with
a sexy older woman?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:38.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's important, too,
but it's not the main thing.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:41.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm traveling
with you for this.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:41.860 --> 00:13:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An old friend.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:43.450 --> 00:13:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He left my village
ten years ago,</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's time we saw
each other again.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember you
telling us about him.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:49.410 --> 00:13:50.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:50.960 --> 00:13:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A photo?</b></Default>

c0000242
00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:53.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, these are rare.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:55.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
A mage came through town.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He agreed to take this photo
of the two of us.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:59.420 --> 00:14:01.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Do you have any leads
on where he went?</b></Default>

c0000246
00:14:01.590 --> 00:14:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems we're following
the same roads.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:05.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've actually met
several people who've seen him.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:08.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Northern Lands are
much smaller than they look.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:10.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can probably
keep going north</b></Default>

c0000250
00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:12.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and run into him eventually.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:14:15.810 --> 00:14:17.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was ten years ago.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:14:17.270 --> 00:14:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised so many people
remember seeing him.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:14:20.070 --> 00:14:22.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, he's the type
to leave an impression.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And he has a unique name.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:14:24.820 --> 00:14:26.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, really? What is it then?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:14:26.910 --> 00:14:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goes by Gorilla Warrior.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] Huh?
-[FRIEREN] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000258
00:14:32.410 --> 00:14:33.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:14:34.710 --> 00:14:36.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is his real name?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:14:36.590 --> 00:14:37.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:14:38.340 --> 00:14:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His real name?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:14:39.510 --> 00:14:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Are you sure you guys
were best friends?</b></Default>

c0000263
00:14:42.050 --> 00:14:44.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I called him Gorilla Warrior
for years.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:14:44.380 --> 00:14:45.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone in the village did.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:14:45.970 --> 00:14:48.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest, he didn't
give us much of a choice.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:14:48.850 --> 00:14:50.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] And you all just
went along with it?</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:51.390 --> 00:14:52.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:54.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, I'm known
as Goatee Priest.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:55.020 --> 00:14:56.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Even worse.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:56.400 --> 00:14:58.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did people call you that
before you were a priest</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:58.610 --> 00:14:59.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a goatee?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:59.730 --> 00:15:01.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe
we're still talking about this.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:03.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His real name doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:15:03.950 --> 00:15:06.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People will remember
the one he chose for himself.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:15:06.780 --> 00:15:09.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I guarantee he wouldn't let
them call him anything else.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:15:10.120 --> 00:15:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This guy sounds really weird.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:15:11.830 --> 00:15:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:15:13.370 --> 00:15:14.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Weirdest guy I've met.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:22.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000280
00:15:23.050 --> 00:15:24.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Once we cross the canyon,</b></Default>

c0000281
00:15:24.420 --> 00:15:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's about one more week
to Auberst.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:15:26.840 --> 00:15:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pretty soon, we'll finally
be in the magical city.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:33.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This leg of our journey
has felt so long.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:15:33.350 --> 00:15:34.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And for once, I'm blameless.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:15:35.560 --> 00:15:36.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Usually it's my fault,</b></Default>

c0000286
00:15:36.730 --> 00:15:38.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I didn't do
anything wrong this time.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:41.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Would you mind if we
make a stop in this village?</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:42.070 --> 00:15:44.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The road branches, and I'd like
to know which path to follow.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:45.190 --> 00:15:46.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:47.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we could all
use a little break.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[kids grunting]</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:52.790 --> 00:15:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
Excuse me.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:53.870 --> 00:15:55.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did someone
who went by Gorilla</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:55.660 --> 00:15:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>pass through here
in the past ten years?</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:57.880 --> 00:15:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 16C]
That's a wild question.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:59.790 --> 00:16:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! You mean
Mister Gorilla Warrior.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:16:02.550 --> 00:16:03.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
He knows him.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:16:03.710 --> 00:16:05.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the type
to leave an impression,</b></Default>

c0000299
00:16:05.170 --> 00:16:06.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and he has such a unique name.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:16:07.300 --> 00:16:10.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a long time ago, but he
defeated a monster for us.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:16:10.930 --> 00:16:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't happen to know</b></Default>

c0000302
00:16:11.970 --> 00:16:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where he went
after that, would you?</b></Default>

c0000303
00:16:13.720 --> 00:16:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a little harder
to recall.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:16:16.770 --> 00:16:19.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh. Mister Gorilla had
a pretty good relationship</b></Default>

c0000305
00:16:19.900 --> 00:16:22.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the stubborn old woman
who lives up on the plateau.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should try asking her.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:16:24.110 --> 00:16:26.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Stubborn old woman?</b></Default>

c0000308
00:16:26.490 --> 00:16:27.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a rude nickname.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:28.990 --> 00:16:31.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a stubborn old woman,
as you can see.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:31.950 --> 00:16:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not telling you
for free, son.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:34.580 --> 00:16:36.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I guess
she calls herself that.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do we have to do?</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:38.870 --> 00:16:43.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:43.130 --> 00:16:44.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can think of a few things
you can do</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:45.050 --> 00:16:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to earn the information.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First, you will deliver
this letter</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:48.970 --> 00:16:50.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to a man named Nagel.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:50.550 --> 00:16:53.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a blacksmith
in the neighboring town.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:55.600 --> 00:16:57.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't know she'd have us
running errands.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:57.810 --> 00:16:59.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It reminds me of my adventures
with Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:17:00.730 --> 00:17:02.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You did things like this
with the great Hero?</b></Default>

c0000322
00:17:03.690 --> 00:17:05.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Helping people
with ordinary tasks</b></Default>

c0000323
00:17:05.690 --> 00:17:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was a daily occurrence for us.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:17:07.860 --> 00:17:09.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And most of the time,
those errands evolved</b></Default>

c0000325
00:17:09.860 --> 00:17:11.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into troublesome hunts</b></Default>

c0000326
00:17:11.110 --> 00:17:12.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for either treasure
or monsters.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:17:12.990 --> 00:17:15.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Oh! Please,
don't jinx us like that.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Monsters or not,
we should do everything we can</b></Default>

c0000329
00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to get her to open up to us.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:17:21.170 --> 00:17:28.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000331
00:17:47.780 --> 00:17:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] This stubborn old woman
just refuses to open up to us.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:17:51.200 --> 00:17:53.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I'm starting to see why
everyone calls her that now.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:55.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:17:55.530 --> 00:17:56.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Himmel or Heiter were here,</b></Default>

c0000335
00:17:56.910 --> 00:17:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>convincing her to talk to us
would have only taken hours.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:18:00.290 --> 00:18:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's too bad that
everyone in our party</b></Default>

c0000337
00:18:02.330 --> 00:18:03.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is socially awkward.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STUBBORN]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:18:06.000 --> 00:18:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:18:07.500 --> 00:18:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's one more thing.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:18:09.010 --> 00:18:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going to polish
the statue of the heroes</b></Default>

c0000342
00:18:11.630 --> 00:18:12.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the canyon.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:18:14.010 --> 00:18:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come with me.
I'll show you the way.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:18:18.140 --> 00:18:19.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I'd like to know
about the statue.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:18:20.100 --> 00:18:22.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STUBBORN] It's a stone carving
of the heroes</b></Default>

c0000346
00:18:22.230 --> 00:18:24.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that supposedly saved
the whole world</b></Default>

c0000347
00:18:24.730 --> 00:18:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a long time ago.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:28.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's all I know
about the thing.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:18:29.320 --> 00:18:31.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A couple of forgotten heroes.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:18:31.190 --> 00:18:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one even knows their names.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:33.070 --> 00:18:35.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we've looked after it
for generations.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:36.070 --> 00:18:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A couple
of forgotten heroes, huh?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:38.790 --> 00:18:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Speaking of names, young man,
you're Goatee Priest, right?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:42.160 --> 00:18:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:43.670 --> 00:18:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you know about that?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:45.540 --> 00:18:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:48.800 --> 00:18:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STUBBORN]
Here. This is the statue.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:52.670 --> 00:18:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
A priest and a warrior.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:55.340 --> 00:18:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's older than I thought
it would be.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:57.680 --> 00:18:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] They bear
a striking resemblance</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:59.310 --> 00:19:00.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Mister Sein
and Mister Gorilla.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:19:01.270 --> 00:19:03.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I recognize
the warrior.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm not sure how.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:19:05.600 --> 00:19:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

c0000365
00:19:06.860 --> 00:19:08.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's a statue of Kraft.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000366
00:19:09.360 --> 00:19:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Whoa! You're right.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:19:10.780 --> 00:19:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
It looks just like him.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:17.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we should get started
while there's light.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:20.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:19:20.410 --> 00:19:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000371
00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sein?
-[SEIN] I see.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:19:26.250 --> 00:19:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, the warrior's
name is Kraft.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:29.630 --> 00:19:30.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And this one?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:30.670 --> 00:19:32.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I'm sorry. I don't know.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:33.670 --> 00:19:34.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no matter.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:39.050 --> 00:19:40.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
What's this statue?</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:40.760 --> 00:19:42.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't they look just like us?</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:42.850 --> 00:19:44.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GORILLA WARRIOR]
Aw, according to the chief,</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:44.850 --> 00:19:47.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>these guys were a duo
of ancient heroes.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:47.560 --> 00:19:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But nobody I talked to
remembers their names.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:50.610 --> 00:19:52.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We won't end up
like that, though.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:55.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our legend won't be
an easy one to forget.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:55.610 --> 00:19:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:56.530 --> 00:19:57.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GORILLA WARRIOR]
I'm going to change the world</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:57.910 --> 00:20:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like Himmel and become
an unforgettable hero.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:02.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000388
00:20:03.080 --> 00:20:04.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's our fate to be forgotten.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:20:04.790 --> 00:20:06.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even the most vibrant stories
will fade.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:20:07.540 --> 00:20:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel did amazing things
with his time in this world,</b></Default>

c0000391
00:20:10.460 --> 00:20:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but his story is no different.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:20:12.210 --> 00:20:13.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:20:14.130 --> 00:20:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, when you put it that way,</b></Default>

c0000394
00:20:15.970 --> 00:20:17.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it sounds impossible
to make a mark.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:20.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:21.100 --> 00:20:22.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I could have
muscles like that</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I worked out hard enough?</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:27.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got a new name.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:28.560 --> 00:20:30.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From now on,
call me Gorilla Warrior!</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:32.230 --> 00:20:33.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:33.400 --> 00:20:34.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would we do that?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:35.230 --> 00:20:37.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because if I want to become
an unforgettable hero,</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:37.900 --> 00:20:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I need
a more memorable name.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:40.490 --> 00:20:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm?
-[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:43.410 --> 00:20:45.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A strange approach,
but it's worth a try.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:45.830 --> 00:20:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh.
-Goatee Priest.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:49.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, how's that
for unforgettable?</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:49.670 --> 00:20:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:52.210 --> 00:20:55.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
That's a great name!</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:56.380 --> 00:20:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] You should
grow one when you can.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:58.380 --> 00:20:59.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might look good.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:59.550 --> 00:21:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000413
00:21:02.970 --> 00:21:05.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000414
00:21:05.430 --> 00:21:06.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
We're finally done.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:08.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was a lot of work.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:21:09.100 --> 00:21:10.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
If only it was a bronze statue.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:10.980 --> 00:21:12.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could have used a spell.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:12.770 --> 00:21:15.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STUBBORN] I made Gorilla
polish it, too, a while back.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:19.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You lot did a much better job
of it than he did, though.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fighting is pretty much
all he's good for.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:23.200 --> 00:21:24.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever else
you say about him,</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:24.830 --> 00:21:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his name sure was memorable.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:27.330 --> 00:21:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:29.250 --> 00:21:31.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gorilla talked about you
all the time.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His friend, Goatee Priest.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said the two of you
would become heroes</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:36.340 --> 00:21:38.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>whose names would be
remembered forever.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:39.170 --> 00:21:40.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Foolish.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:40.260 --> 00:21:47.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000430
00:22:00.610 --> 00:22:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you figure out
where Gorilla went?</b></Default>

c0000431
00:22:04.410 --> 00:22:05.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Tur.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:22:06.410 --> 00:22:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a trading city</b></Default>

c0000433
00:22:07.410 --> 00:22:08.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the middle
of the Northern Lands.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:22:09.540 --> 00:22:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] That's a long way
to the east from here.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:22:12.250 --> 00:22:14.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's in the opposite
direction of Auberst.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:22:16.170 --> 00:22:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[STARK] Huh.
-[FERN] Huh.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I gonna do now?</b></Default>

c0000439
00:23:56.440 --> 00:23:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I need to speak with
each of you, one at a time.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:00.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Being a peacemaker
is a priest's job.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:24:00.770 --> 00:24:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You're embarrassing me.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:24:02.570 --> 00:24:03.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
I guess it's not so bad.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:05.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take care, then.</b></Default>

